	measure 'Total Failed Items' = ```
			
			    COALESCE(
			        CALCULATE( SUM(data_quality_testing[RESULT]),
			        data_quality_testing[PASS_FLAG] = FALSE()),
			        0)
			```
		formatString: #,0
